property.name: displayText
property.value: You can collect items like coins or shields by moving close to them

property.name: displayText
property.value: Some objects can be destroyed. Try to hit them using the left mouse key or the controller button B.

property.name: displayText
property.value: To fight enemies you need to get close to them to hit them with your mighty battle axe! But if you come close to enemies they will also try to hit you. So try to defend yourself with your shield. To use the shield press the right mouse button or the controller button A.

property.name: displayText
property.value: After fighthing an enemy your HP and Shield might be lowered. To recharge them use health or shield items. There might be some in this cheest. Open it using the E key or the controller button Y.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Dwarfs are known to be mighty wariors and the greatest blacksmithes in all nine worlds. But they are no gread swimmers. So stay away from water.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Some enemies are stronger than others. They can take more damage and deal more damage to you. They also behave different. But all of them have one thing in common. They can be killed!

property.name: displayText
property.value: To get rid of bats the spin attack is very usefull. To activate it, push and hold down the left mouse button or the controller button B, till you hear a sound that indicates that the attack is charged. Then release the attack button and use the spin attack to crush your enemies!

property.name: displayText
property.value: You can run faster for some time by pushing the shift key or by pushing down the analog stick of the controller. But that will cost endurance. If you have no endurance left you can not run faster anymore and can not attack for some time.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Arrows can be used to attack distant enemies. To use arrows they have to be chosen in the pause menu. Use the escape key or the controller button 'start' to open the menu. They can be shot using the space key or the controller button X.

property.name: displayText
property.value: Some pathes may be blocked. You'll need a key to unlock it. Most of these doors can be unlocked by any key (that was found in the same level). But some require special keys.
